<i>Kau juga.</i>

719
00:58:30,882 --> 00:58:32,300
Na-bi.

720
00:58:33,218 --> 00:58:34,636
- Hai.
- Hai.

721
00:58:43,311 --> 00:58:44,688
Tidurmu nyenyak?

722
00:58:44,771 --> 00:58:47,774
- Ya. Kau?
- Aku juga.

723
00:58:47,858 --> 00:58:49,192
- Berangkat?
- Ya.

724
00:59:41,787 --> 00:59:43,538
- Pak.
- Ya?

725
00:59:43,622 --> 00:59:44,706
Bisa jaga sepeda kami?

726
00:59:44,790 --> 00:59:47,000
-Ya. Tentu saja.
